snippet.title: EverQuest II Altar of Malice Expansion [OFFICIAL TRAILER]
snippet.description:
Buy Altar of Malice now at https://www.everquest2.com/expansion-content

Introducing EQII's 11th Expansion, Altar of Malice!  You can now level to 100 and experience brand new content such as Phantom and Tranquil Sea.  Don't miss out on the new Grandmaster Spells and the amazing in-game items!
